<h2 style="font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; color: #333; text-align: center;">New Request Notification</h2>
<p style="margin-bottom: 10px;">Hello <%= SVAgentName %>,</p>
<p style="margin-bottom: 10px;">A new request has been submitted and requires your review.</p>
<p style="margin-bottom: 10px;">
    Request ID: <strong style="color: #0056b3;">"<%= request_id %>"</strong> <br>
    Request Type: <strong style="color: #0056b3;">"<%= requestType %>"</strong></p>
<p style="margin-bottom: 10px;">
    <a href="<%= baseUrl %>/tickets/<%= request_id %>" 
        style="display: inline-block; padding: 10px 20px; font-size: 14px; font-family: Arial, sans-serif; color: #fff; text-decoration: none; background-color: #0056b3; border-radius: 5px;">
        View Request Details
    </a>
</p>
<p style="margin-bottom: 10px;">Here are some more details:</p>
<ul style="font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; color: #333333; padding-left: 20px;">
    <li style="color: #555555; margin-bottom: 5px;">Requested By Agent: <%= agentEmailRequested %>, (ID: " <%= agentIdRequested %>")</li>
</ul>
<p style="margin-bottom: 10px;">Please review this request as soon as possible and update its status in the system.</p>
